nodes.text: Star Wars Jedi Master Magazine 2 is the second issue of Star Wars Jedi Master Magazine. It was published by Titan Magazines on January 19, 2016.

Continue on the path to becoming a Jedi Knight in the new Star Wars Jedi Master Magazine! Packed with fascinating features, fact files and puzzles, each issue prepares Padawans for the journey ahead by teaching them about pivotal events in Jedi history in the run-up to the release of Star Wars: The Force Awakens! This issue, learn everything you need to know about Bounty Hunters!
